videos.description: Anfernee McLemore swats away a layup attempt, and it goes right to Bryce Brown, who  spins away from Marcus Lytle for the fast-break finish.
videos.headline: McLemore's big block leads to transition bucket

videos.description: Samir Doughty finds a cutting Anfernee McLemore, who gets through the contact and throws down a posterizing slam on Davy Fisher.
videos.headline: McLemore dunks all over Fisher for and-1

videos.description: Malik Dunbar gets a steal and pitches it ahead to J'Von McCormick, who rises up for a big two-handed jam to make it 48-26 Tigers heading into halftime.
videos.headline: Auburn caps off 1st half with steal and slam

videos.description: Brandon Boston tries to finish in transition, but Chuma Okeke protects the rim and sends it back off the glass.
videos.headline: Okeke swats Boston on fast break

videos.description: Bryce Brown is off the mark on a 3-pointer, but Horace Spencer is there to grab the board and power back up for a two-handed finish.
videos.headline: Spencer throws down putback jam

videos.description: Horace Spencer outlets to Myles Parker, who takes it himself and elevates for an authoritative one-handed flush to make it 98-45 Auburn.
videos.headline: Parker puts on exclamation point with huge slam

videos.description: J'Von McCormick steals and slams, then Horace Spencer forces a turnover and lobs it up to Malik Dunbar for a strong alley-oop finish.
videos.headline: Tigers pour it on with back-to-back dunks
